法瑞尔·威廉姆斯向我们讲述他的乐高传记片《逐片》：“这对我来说是一次奇妙的历史经历” https://www.nme.com/news/music/pharrell-williams-morgan-neville-interview-trailer-lego-piece-by-piece-3762433?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=pharrell-williams-morgan-neville-采访预告片乐高逐件Kyann-Sian WilliamsThu, 06 Jun 2024 14:00:27 +0000Film InterviewsFilm NewsMusic InterviewsMusic NewsNewsHip-hopRap https://www.nme.com/?p=3762433 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/pharrell-@-2000-x-1270-Edward-Berthelot_Getty-Images.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="法瑞尔·威廉姆斯 (Pharrell Williams) 亮相 2024/2025 秋冬巴黎时装周。图片来源：Edward Berthelot/Getty Images" decoding="async" fetchpriority="high" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/pharrell-@-2000-x-1270-Edward-Berthelot_Getty-Images.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/pharrell-@-2000-x-1270-Edward-Berthelot_Getty-Images-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/pharrell-@-2000-x-1270-Edward-Berthelot_Getty-Images-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/pharrell-@-2000-x-1270-Edward-Berthelot_Getty-Images-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/pharrell-@-2000-x-1270-Edward-Berthelot_Getty-Images-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/pharrell-@-2000-x-1270-Edward-Berthelot_Getty-Images-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>在这里查看这部电影的预告片，法瑞尔和导演摩根·内维尔向《NME》讲述“一部纪录片、传记片、动画电影和音乐剧”</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/pharrell-williams-morgan-neville-interview-trailer-lego-piece-by-piece-3762433">法瑞尔·威廉姆斯 (Pharrell Williams) 向我们讲述了他在乐高中的传记片“逐片”：“这对我来说是一段令人惊叹的历史经历”，该</a>帖子首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/pharrell-@-2000-x-1270-Edward-Berthelot_Getty-Images.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="法瑞尔·威廉姆斯 (Pharrell Williams) 亮相 2024/2025 秋冬巴黎时装周。图片来源：Edward Berthelot/Getty Images" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/pharrell-@-2000-x-1270-Edward-Berthelot_Getty-Images.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/pharrell-@-2000-x-1270-Edward-Berthelot_Getty-Images-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/pharrell-@-2000-x-1270-Edward-Berthelot_Getty-Images-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/pharrell-@-2000-x-1270-Edward-Berthelot_Getty-Images-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/pharrell-@-2000-x-1270-Edward-Berthelot_Getty-Images-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/pharrell-@-2000-x-1270-Edward-Berthelot_Getty-Images-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p><a href="/artists/pharrell-williams">法瑞尔·威廉姆斯 (Pharrell Williams)</a>和导演摩根·内维尔 (Morgan Neville) 接受<em>NME</em>采访，谈论了<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/pharrell-announces-his-biopic-will-be-made-out-of-lego-3578112">前者即将上映的乐高动画传记片<em>《Piece By Piece</em> 》</a> 。请观看下面我们的采访以及预告片。</p><p>今年十月，一部基于威廉姆斯职业生涯的新电影将在电影院上映。这部电影将追随这位多产的创意博学者的崛起，并重现他一生中的重要时刻，例如他与查德·雨果一起在制作人团体<a href="/artists/the-neptunes">“海王星”</a>中的时光，与<a href="/artists/snoop-dogg">史努比狗狗</a>和<a href="/artists/gwen-stefani">格温·史蒂芬妮</a>的合作等等。</p><p>今天，该项目的预告片已经发布。该剪辑以乐高版本的威廉姆斯和内维尔进行坐下来采访开始，然后切入电影中的场景。您可以听到这位“美丽”明星讲述他的职业生涯亮点，还可以看到威廉姆斯过去著名合作者的客串。 </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/reel/C74HrZ8pwqk/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-rad