 MC5 宣布推出 53 年来首张新专辑《Heavy Lifting》 https://www.nme.com/news/music/mc5-announce-heavy-lifting-their-first-new-album-in-53-years-preorder-3763269?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=mc5-announce-重磅推出他们 53 年来首张新专辑的预购Liberty DunworthThu, 06 Jun 2024 12:25:37 +0000 Music NewsNewsRockhttps://www.nme.com/?p=3763269 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/MC5-press@2000x1270.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="韦恩·克莱默和鲍勃·埃兹林。" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/MC5-press@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/MC5-press@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/MC5-press@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/MC5-press@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/MC5-press@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/MC5-press@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>它由 Tom Morello、Slash 等人贡献，主打单曲“Boys Who Play With Matches”于今天（6 月 6 日）发行</p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/mc5-announce-heavy-lifting-their-first-new-album-in-53-years-preorder-3763269">MC5 宣布“Heavy Lifting”后，他们 53 年来的第一张新专辑</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/MC5-press@2000x1270.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="韦恩·克莱默和鲍勃·埃兹林。" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/MC5-press@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/MC5-press@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/MC5-press@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/MC5-press@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/MC5-press@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/MC5-press@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/mc5">MC5</a>分享了“Heavy Lifting”的详细信息，这是他们五十多年来的第一张新录音室专辑。看看下面的主打单曲“玩火柴的男孩”。</p><p>今天（6 月 6 日）宣布，该项目将由创始成员韦恩·克莱默 (Wayne Kramer) 担任吉他手和主唱，以及一些特别客串。</p><p>弗莱默在过去的五年里与乐队一起工作，成果丰硕，是乐队中最后一位活跃的成员。<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/mc5-co-founder-wayne-kramer-has-died-3581827">他在与胰腺癌作斗争后于二月去世，享年 75 岁</a>。在他去世之前，他与奥克兰歌手兼作曲家布拉德·布鲁克斯 (Brad Brooks) 共同创作了即将发行的专辑中的 13 首歌曲中的 12 首。</p><p>鼓手 Dennis &#39;Machine Gun&#39; Thompson<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/mc5-drummer-dennis-thompson-has-died-age-75-3755041">在五月去世</a>前不久也为即将发行的唱片做出了贡献。这将是他最后一次录音室录音。</p><p>这张专辑将于 10 月 18 日发行，这是 MC5 自 53 年前推出《High Time》以来分享的第一张完整专辑。</p><p> “它非常重，”制片人鲍勃·埃兹林说。 “它传达了革命性的信息，但也充满了幽默感。有一点重金属的味道。有相当多的恐惧。但这是一张沉重的唱片，它是一张左、右、中的吉他唱片。” </p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="MC5 - “玩火柴的男孩”（官方音频）" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/wl3NMXG_shI?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p> “大多数时候只是一堵吉他墙，主要是由韦恩和他的精神驱动的，”他补充道。 “这是一个吉他手巅峰时期的快照。我们都感到有责任确保他的作品被听到，他受到赞扬。我们为这个项目倾注了全部心血。”</p><p>聆听上面的主打单曲“玩火柴的男孩”。</p><p>去年 11 月，克莱默在接受 Uncut 采访时谈到了这个项目。 “长寿并保持创造力。这就是我的态度。这张专辑是从《High Time》结束的地方继续的。在这一点上，我认为艺术家有责任反映他们正在经历的时代，”他当时告诉媒体。 “我认为我们制作的专辑与我们今天的处境和我们面临的挑战同步，并且传达了积极的信息。”</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/mc5-announce-first-album-over-50-years-us-tour-dates-3179197">自 2022 年以来，MC5 就一直在预告这张新专辑</a>，当时乐队在 Instagram 上分享了朋克老将的旧镜头以及主打歌《Heavy Lifting》的片段。</p><p>现在，已确认该唱片将由<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/rage-against-the-machine">Rage Against The Machine</a>的<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/tom-morello">Tom Morello</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/slash">Slash</a> 、William Duvall（ <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/alice-in-chains">Alice In Chains</a> ）、Tim McIllrath（ <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/rise-against">Rise Against</a> ）等人客串。</p><p>该专辑的附赠版也将推出，其中收录了<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/soundgarden">Soundgarden</a>吉他手 Kim Thayil、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/fugazi">Fugazi</a>鼓手 Brendan Canty 和主唱 Marcus Durant（Zen Guerrilla）之前未发行的现场录音和表演。<a href="https://mc5.lnk.to/heavyliftingPR" target="_blank" rel="noopener">在此</a>预订专辑并在下面找到曲目列表。 </p><figure id="attachment_3763277" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3763277" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3763277" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/mc5-artwork@2000x2000.jpg" alt="MC5“Heavy Lifting”专辑封面" width="2000" height="1997" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/mc5-artwork@2000x2000.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/mc5-artwork@2000x2000-150x150.jpg 150w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/mc5-artwork@2000x2000-400x399.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/mc5-artwork@2000x2000-800x799.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/mc5-artwork@2000x2000-696x695.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/mc5-artwork@2000x2000-1392x1390.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/mc5-artwork@2000x2000-1068x1066.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3763277" class="wp-caption-text"> MC5“Heavy Lifting”专辑封面。图片来源：新闻界</figcaption></figure><h2><strong>“举重”曲目列表是：</strong></h2><p> <strong>1.“举重”（壮举。汤姆·莫雷洛）</strong><br /> <strong>2.《门口的野蛮人》</strong><br /> <strong>3.“改变，不变”</strong><br /> <strong>4.“弹簧刀的边缘”（壮举威廉·杜瓦尔和 Slash）</strong><br /> <strong>5.“黑靴子”（壮举。蒂姆·麦克II拉斯）</strong><br /> <strong>6.《我很有趣》（骗子）</strong><br /> <strong>7.《二十五英里》</strong><br /> <strong>8.“因为你的车”</strong><br /> <strong>9.《打火柴的男孩》</strong><br /> <strong>10.“盲眼”（壮举。丹尼斯·汤普森）</strong><br /> <strong>11.“找不到”（壮举。弗农·里德和丹尼斯·汤普森）</strong><br /> <strong>12.“祝福释放”</strong><br /> <strong>13.“Hit It Hard”（壮举。乔·贝瑞）</strong></p><p><strong>附加曲目列表（2CD/2LP）：</strong><br /> <strong>1.“兰布林玫瑰”</strong><br /> <strong>2.“排除堵塞”</strong><br /> <strong>3.“走到一起”</strong><br /> <strong>4.“汽车城正在燃烧”</strong><br /> <strong>5.“边界”</strong><br /> <strong>6.“必须继续前进”</strong><br /> <strong>7.“未来/现在”</strong><br /> <strong>8.“毒药”</strong><br /> <strong>9.“震动街”</strong><br /> <strong>10.《安妮姐妹》</strong></p><p> 10 月 18 日的发行日期也是乐队将与<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/ozzy-osbourne">Ozzy Osbourne</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/cher">Cher</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/dave-matthews-band">Dave Matthews Band</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/a-tribe-called-quest">A Tribe Called Quest</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/peter-frampton">Peter Frampton</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/foreigner">Foreigner</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/kool-the-gang">Kool &amp; The</a>一起入选<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/rock-roll-hall-of-fame-2024-ozzy-osbourne-cher-and-more-to-be-inducted-3749163">2024 年摇滚名人堂的</a>前一天。<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/kool-the-gang">冈</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/mary-j-blige">玛丽·J·布莱姬</a>。</p><p>除了克莱默和汤普森双双去世外， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/former-mc5-manager-john-sinclair-has-died-aged-82-3612369">乐队前任经理约翰·辛克莱也在今年四月意外去世</a>。</p><p>他的代表马特·李证实了这位 82 岁诗人和政治活动家因充血性心力衰竭在底特律接收医院去世的消息。</p><p>辛克莱是一位有影响力的活动家，他因推动美国大麻合法化以及在 MC5 中的角色而闻名。这位戴维森人也是民权捍卫者，也是激进反种族主义组织白豹党的联合创始人。</p><p>这位已故活动家还帮助创办了<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/iggy-and-the-stooges">Iggy Pop And The Stooges</a> 。<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/iggy-pop">波普</a>是辛克莱去世后最先向他表示哀悼的人之一。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/mc5-announce-heavy-lifting-their-first-new-album-in-53-years-preorder-3763269">MC5 宣布“Heavy Lifting”后，他们 53 年来的第一张新专辑</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
汉斯·齐默 (Hans Zimmer)、西尔 (Seal) 等人宣布成为安德烈亚·波切利 (Andrea Bocelli) 在伦敦 BST 海德公园 2024 年的特邀嘉宾https://www.nme.com/news/music/hans-zimmer-seal-and-more-announced-as-special-guests-for-andrea-bocelli-at-londons-bst-hyde-park-2024- 3763248?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=hans-zimmer-seal-and-more-announced-as-special-guests-for-andrea-bocelli-at-londons-bst-hyde-park-2024Tom Skinner Thu, 06 Jun 2024 12:12:24 +0000 Music NewsNewsLive Music NewsPophttps://www.nme.com/?p=3763248 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/AndreaBocelli-BST-Hyde-Park-London-Hans-Zimmer-Seal-special-guests-announced.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="Hans Zimmer（左）、Andrea Bocelli（中）和 Seal（右）的三张并排图像" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/AndreaBocelli-BST-Hyde-Park-London-Hans-Zimmer-Seal-special-guests-announced.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/AndreaBocelli-BST-Hyde-Park-London-Hans-Zimmer-Seal-special-guests-announced-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/AndreaBocelli-BST-Hyde-Park-London-Hans-Zimmer-Seal-special-guests-announced-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/AndreaBocelli-BST-Hyde-Park-London-Hans-Zimmer-Seal-special-guests-announced-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/AndreaBocelli-BST-Hyde-Park-London-Hans-Zimmer-Seal-special-guests-announced-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/AndreaBocelli-BST-Hyde-Park-London-Hans-Zimmer-Seal-special-guests-announced-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>这位古典歌手下个月将在首都庆祝他的职业生涯30周年</p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/hans-zimmer-seal-and-more-announced-as-special-guests-for-andrea-bocelli-at-londons-bst-hyde-park-2024-3763248">汉斯·季默 (Hans Zimmer)、西尔 (Seal) 等人宣布作为安德烈·波切利 (Andrea Bocelli) 在 2024 年伦敦 BST 海德公园的特邀嘉宾，这一</a>消息首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/AndreaBocelli-BST-Hyde-Park-London-Hans-Zimmer-Seal-special-guests-announced.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="Hans Zimmer（左）、Andrea Bocelli（中）和 Seal（右）的三张并排图像" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/AndreaBocelli-BST-Hyde-Park-London-Hans-Zimmer-Seal-special-guests-announced.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/AndreaBocelli-BST-Hyde-Park-London-Hans-Zimmer-Seal-special-guests-announced-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/AndreaBocelli-BST-Hyde-Park-London-Hans-Zimmer-Seal-special-guests-announced-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/AndreaBocelli-BST-Hyde-Park-London-Hans-Zimmer-Seal-special-guests-announced-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/AndreaBocelli-BST-Hyde-Park-London-Hans-Zimmer-Seal-special-guests-announced-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/AndreaBocelli-BST-Hyde-Park-London-Hans-Zimmer-Seal-special-guests-announced-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/hans-zimmer">汉斯·齐默 (Hans Zimmer</a> )、<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/seal">西尔 (Seal</a> ) 等人已被宣布为<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/andrea-bocelli-announced-first-headline-act-bst-hyde-park-2024-buy-tickets-3535927">Andrea Bocelli 在 BST 海德公园 2024 年的头条秀的</a>特邀嘉宾。请参阅下面的阵容。</p><p>这位著名的古典歌手将于 7 月 5 日星期五在<a href="https://www.nme.com/festivals/british-summer-time-bst-festival">伦敦系列音乐会上</a>亮相。这场演出被誉为“英国独有”的演出，这将标志着 BST 首次由古典音乐家担任主角。</p><p>今天（6 月 6 日），组织者透露了波切利即将在海德公园举行的演出中与波切利一起登上舞台的众多表演者，这场演出标志着他职业生涯的 30 周年。其中包括前面提到的 Zimmer 和 Seal，以及 Zucchero、Loren Allred、Joaquina、Andrea Griminelli、Rusanda Panfili 和 Bocelli 12 岁的女儿 Virginia。</p><p>他们与皇家爱乐乐团（由米歇尔·斯波蒂指挥）、舞者安吉丽卡·吉斯蒙多和弗朗西斯科·科斯塔一起出现在阵容中。</p><p>该法案的新成员加入了先前宣布的凯瑟琳·詹金斯和波切利的儿子马特奥（他们都将表演自己的独家表演），主持人米琳·克拉斯，纳丁·塞拉，伊莎贝尔·伦纳德和卢卡·米凯莱蒂，以及克劳奇结束节日合唱团。 </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/p/C73lIifiyVQ/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-right: 14px; width: 40px;"></div><div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; flex-grow: 1; justify-content: center;"><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; margin-bottom: 6px; width: 100px;"></div><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; width: 60px;"></div></div></div><div style="padding: 19% 0;"></div><div style="display:block; height:50px; margin:0 auto 12px; width:50px;"><svg width="50px" height="50px" viewBox="0 0 60 60" version="1.1" xmlns="https://www.w3.org/2000/svg" xmlns:xlink="https://www.w3.org/1999/xlink"><g stroke="none" stroke-width="1" fill="none" fill-rule="evenodd"><g transform="translate(-511.000000, -20.000000)" fill="#000000"><g><path d="M556.869,30.41 C554.814,30.41 553.148,32.076 553.148,34.131 C553.148,36.186 554.814,37.852 556.869,37.852 C558.924,37.852 560.59,36.186 560.59,34.131 C560.59,32.076 558.924,30.41 556.869,30.41 M541,60.657 C535.114,60.657 530.342,55.887 530.342,50 C530.342,44.114 535.114,39.342 541,39.342 C546.887,39.342 551.658,44.114 551.658,50 C551.658,55.887 546.887,60.657 541,60.657 M541,33.886 C532.1,33.886 524.886,41.1 524.886,50 C524.886,58.899 532.1,66.113 541,66.113 C549.9,66.113 557.115,58.899 557.115,50 C557.115,41.1 549.9,33.886 541,33.886 M565.378,62.101 C565.244,65.022 564.756,66.606 